Team,
Per our call today within the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA) 11.6.0.113 for the zSandbox > DLMembership11 Job the issue was that the ADI job was not longer collecting the Extended Attribute of the “physicalDe1iveryOfficeName”.

With this corrected in the Jobs >> .Active Directory Inventory>> 1-AD_Scan Query and the SA_ADInventory_ExtendedAttributesPivotView correctly populated post the next full job run.

I will spin off a new case for the FSAC jobs post finding that a needed port is being blocked (8766)

Thank You for the update, I will close out this ticket as noted.

We have 30days to reopen once the closure email is received.

To reopen we can just reply to that email to bring the case back into my queue.
